      </ReturnValue>
      <Docs>
        <since version=".NET 2.0" />
        <summary>
          <attribution license="cc4" from="Microsoft" modified="false" />
          <para>The control grows as much as necessary to fit its contents but does not shrink smaller than the value of its <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Size" />   property. The form can be resized, but cannot be made so small that any of its contained controls are hidden.</para>
        </summary>
      </Docs>
